/**
 * Mock demo dataset — the live source of truth the Zustand store is seeded from.
 *
 * Fully deterministic (fixed ids, dates derived from DEMO_TODAY, no Date.now/random) so
 * server render and client hydration agree. Flags are GENERATED by running the engine over
 * each patient's data as of DEMO_TODAY — never hand-authored — so seeded flags match what
 * the live engine would produce.
 *
 * Cast: one HERO (Maria Reyes, week-10 MTX) plus six supporting patients producing a
 * realistic spread of ~9 open flags across severities. The hero's three-flag flare lands
 * at runtime via the "Simulate hero flare check-in" demo control (see scenarios.ts).
 */

